<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE paragraph PUBLIC "-//IFRS//DTD DITA Paragraph//EN" "../../../DocTypes/com.ifrs.doctype/dtd/paragraph.dtd"><paragraph id="IAS08_36" base="SL29873" principles="yes"><paranum class="- topic/title paragraph/paranum "/><titlealts><navtitle>36</navtitle></titlealts><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS&#xa0;8"/><data name="paranum" value="36"/></prolog><body outputclass="bold"><p id="IAS08_P0128">The effect of a <ph>change in an </ph><xref href="IAS08_5.dita#IAS08_5/IAS08_5_accountingestimates">accounting estimate<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_accountingestimates"/></ph></xref>, other than a change to which <xref id="IAS08_X0159" base="A8-114" href="IAS08_37.dita#IAS08_37">paragraph 37</xref> applies, shall be recognised prospectively by including it in profit or loss in: </p><ol outputclass="static" id="IAS08_L0021" base="SL141554" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value>       <p id="IAS08_P0129" base="SL141556">the period of the change, if the change affects that period only; or</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value>       <p id="IAS08_P0130" base="SL141558">the period of the change and future periods, if the change affects both.</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>